title: Девушка с венком
author: Богданова Татьяна
description:
The painting is one of the 'Girls-Deserts' collection pieces. This one is done with oil on canvas. 'A Maiden with Wreath' is related to symbolic realism being a representative of portraits genre. 

This artwork took part in one exhibition approved by corresponding certificate.

Pay attention: Upon buying the digitalized copy of this masterpiece in Ultra HD 1:1 resolution, you will receive the original physical Authentic Painting.
